 
<p>
*Monopolists <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/views/2022/07/15/why-food-prices-are-rising-even-more">control nearly every part of the food production process</a>.*
And they are driving up food prices.
<p>
When the government regulators permitted these mergers, they were
abandoning their mission.  This was obvious, but democracy in the
US had been undermined to the point where we could not get anyone
to stop it.

 